data.description: ON the ever popular Sun River golf course in Utah's #1 Active Adult Community. NEW CARPET throughout, sprawling, open floor plan with generous sized rooms, lots of storage, great to entertain being proud to come home to and hate to leave. The outside is just as beautiful with a peaceful ambiance including and extended covered back patio, in-ground hot tub with waterfall feature and mature landscape foliage. Exterior recently repainted + artificial grass so sell the lawn mower!! More features pointed out in the home.
